This map is based off of "backalley_run_b2", it is basically the terrorists in one house/location and they have scoutz to shoot the ct's. The cts can scavage for some guns and nades to distract the t's while trying to reach their goal. The goal is to make it to the t's and kill them with those god damn TMPS and Grenades!

Hope you have fun, please rate. BTW its alpha!
